<typeStatus id="845E880C4D242638FF44FA34660BFA67" box="[151,261,1437,1461]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">paratypes</typeStatus>
, pale brown; tunic papillated with sediment particles abundant, densely packed, completely covering body wall; anterior region not bent ventrally. Larger capitate papillae arranged in transverse rows, one per segment dorsally (
<figureCitation id="C3DE2A2B4D242638FED0FA4D6649FA2E" box="[259,327,1508,1532]" captionStart="FIGURE 9" captionStartId="23.[151,250,1834,1857]" captionTargetBox="[175,1411,810,1806]" captionTargetId="figure@23.[169,1417,805,1814]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="FIGURE 9. Piromis suni n. sp. A. Holotype (SMF- 15348), without posterior end, dorsal view. B. Same, anterior end, dorsal view. C. Same, anterior end, ventral view. D. Paratype, series of notochaeta from chaetiger 31, showing different article length in basal, medial and distal parts. E. Same, neurochaetae from chaetiger 11. F. Holotype, neurochaetae from chaetiger 31. Scale bars: A: 2 mm, B – C: 0.5 mm, D: 75 µm, E, F: 180 µm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/277220/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
Fig. 
<number id="ED2D24894D242638FEEAFA4D6649FA2E" box="[313,327,1508,1532]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="9.0">9</number>
</figureCitation>
B) and ventrally (
<figureCitation id="C3DE2A2B4D242638FDC0FA4D6557FA2E" box="[531,601,1508,1532]" captionStart="FIGURE 9" captionStartId="23.[151,250,1834,1857]" captionTargetBox="[175,1411,810,1806]" captionTargetId="figure@23.[169,1417,805,1814]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="FIGURE 9. Piromis suni n. sp. A. Holotype (SMF- 15348), without posterior end, dorsal view. B. Same, anterior end, dorsal view. C. Same, anterior end, ventral view. D. Paratype, series of notochaeta from chaetiger 31, showing different article length in basal, medial and distal parts. E. Same, neurochaetae from chaetiger 11. F. Holotype, neurochaetae from chaetiger 31. Scale bars: A: 2 mm, B – C: 0.5 mm, D: 75 µm, E, F: 180 µm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/277220/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
Fig. 
<number id="ED2D24894D242638FD99FA4D6557FA2E" box="[586,601,1508,1532]" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" value="9.0">9</number>
</figureCitation>
